        <p>Ocean Tides Performance Group is a consulting firm
          established in 1999. </p>
        <p>Based in Winnipeg, Ocean Tides specializes in organizational
          development levers. </p>
        <p>Outcomes of consulting work include improved employee and
          customer loyalty and increased individual and organizational
          performance.</p>
        <div class="listbox">
          <ul>
            <li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">Creating
