        <p style="margin-top: 35px">Specializing in the retail sector,
          Ocean Tides helps clients create high-performance workplaces
          by establishing work processes and routines (including
          management routines) that lead to performance. Ocean Tides
          works with clients to help set conditions for consistent
          employee and customer experiences that lead to loyalty.</p>
